(Corrects to say Chavez spoke by telephone.)  Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
spoke live by phone on state television today after the Nuevo
Herald newspaper reported that he had undergone emergency
treatment for  kidney failure .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charlie Devereux in  London  at 
 cdevereux3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Philip Sanders at 
 psanders@bloomberg.net . 